DESCRIPTION:Pro Helvetia's Game Design Emerging Talents post-production gra
 nt funds the dissemination and marketing of advanced game-design projects.
  Emerging Talents are studios whose game-design education or company found
 ation dates back less than seven years. Applicants must be legal entities 
