 es a connection to Switzerland (Swiss citizenship\, or permanent residency
  with regular artistic activity in Switzerland)\; not open to practitioner
 s without a Swiss connection. At least 50 percent of participants must be 
 Swiss citizens or permanent residents whose place of work is in Switzerlan
 d. AMOUNT: up to CHF 20\,000\, plus potential individual coaching. Deadlin
 es twice a year: 1 March (23:59 CET) and 1 September (23:59 CEST). Apply v
 ia the Pro Helvetia portal.\n\nOrganisation: Pro Helvetia (Swiss Arts Coun
 cil)\nLocation: Switzerland-based emerging game studios.\nAward: Up to CHF
