 on: Post-production\, dissemination and marketing phase\; deadlines twice 
 yearly (1 March and 1 September).\n\nMore: https://prohelvetia.ch/en/find-
 support/game-design-emerging-talents-post-production?utm_source=artificial
 nouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://prohelvetia.ch/en/find-support/game-design-emerging-talents-pos
 t-production?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Switzerland-based emerging game studios.
